{
  "stem": "1901.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 25.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were not as bad, because I remember we walked once out of camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we pinched potatoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And if that would have happened in other camp, in Auschwitz, they would have shot you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we had them here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We had the potatoes in here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we made it loose.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the potatoes roll out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they hit you on your head, bang, not hard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They didn't hit, and were in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then I worked in Ampfing-- I worked in Ampfing it must be six, seven weeks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But every time when the rail-- when the rails were fixed, they bombed them again-- [LAUGHS] three, four times.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Every time, they were not-- it was not anymore defense.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They lay the bombs down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I talk about end of the war, really.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "That was the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The Americans were over there every day by the-- with the airplanes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I don't know what they bombed, Muhldorf, the railway.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They went up to Austria, I don't know where.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But planes day and night, you could see them going, low.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "There was no defense.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that we knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew it was end.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh yes, we knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know when.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We walked to camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there was nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every day, we hoping and hoping.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew it is nearly finished, but not knowing when.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that went on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I must have been in Ampfing [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a month or more-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] March-- six weeks, five, six weeks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was only working on that railway, more or less, only cleaning the rails, cleaning the rails every day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then bombed again, and cleaning it again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was a lot of work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was heavy, you know, with lifting up rails.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
